Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.09,0:01:34.30,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.51,0:01:37.22,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,手都要凍僵了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.89,0:01:39.76,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我特別怕冷啊
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.90,0:01:47.98,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要用暖寶寶嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.77,0:01:51.57,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 謝謝你
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.03,0:01:52.74,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.91,0:02:02.83,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,冰
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.12,0:02:07.92,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好厚的冰啊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.21,0:02:10.09,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天下雨了嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.63,0:02:18.68,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是想把它帶回家了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.80,0:02:19.93,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒有
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.14,0:02:22.81,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不是小學生
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.10,0:02:26.35,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.69,0:02:32.78,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 西片
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.90,0:02:36.07,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我們來比賽吧
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.53,0:02:39.41,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊 要比什麼啊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.91,0:02:43.16,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,比誰拿到校門口的冰塊更大
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.70,0:02:46.79,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 中途要是冰掉在地上的話就算輸
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.79,0:02:48.42,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.96,0:02:51.71,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.96,0:02:52.96,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你先請
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.55,0:02:56.34,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那我開始了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.55,0:03:01.68,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你拿了大塊的冰誒
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.85,0:03:04.64,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能成功帶到學校就好了哦
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.31,0:03:08.52,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,高木同學 你著急了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.98,0:03:11.48,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 我可是絕不會手滑摔碎冰塊的
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.11,0:03:16.82,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我從小看到冰就一定會帶走
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.90,0:03:18.82,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,手指一點也不怕凍
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.11,0:03:22.83,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我絕不會因為凍手就放下冰塊的
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.87,0:03:27.00,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 對於每天嚴格堅持
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.00,0:03:29.33,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,做被高木同學捉弄回數3倍量的俯臥撐的我來說
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.37,0:03:32.50,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這點冰根本算不了什麼嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.13,0:03:36.71,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就要讓你後悔發起這個心血來潮的比賽
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.17,0:03:39.34,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,高木同學
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.80,0:03:41.51,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天就要輸給我了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.27,0:03:48.77,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.14,0:03:50.69,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.77,0:03:54.52,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺西片拿著大冰塊的樣子
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.57,0:03:56.86,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,像個開心的小學生似的
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.98,0:03:59.65,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼…我才沒有開心呢…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.37,0:04:06.04,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好險
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.45,0:04:09.66,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真可惜呀
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.17,0:04:13.08,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡的高木同學…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.29,0:04:15.17,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,大意了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.42,0:04:18.17,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,原來還有「讓對方的冰塊滑掉」這種作戰嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.80,0:04:22.80,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我絕對不會再掉以輕心了 今天一定要贏
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.60,0:04:27.39,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你那麼用力捏的話 冰塊會裂開哦
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.27,0:04:31.94,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,擔心敵人嗎 你可真從容不迫啊高木同學
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.69,0:04:33.44,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.11,0:04:38.69,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不過的確 不能捏太緊反而捏碎了冰塊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.78,0:04:42.78,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 作為懲罰
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.24,0:04:47.37,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,輸了的人要給贏了的人暖手哦 明白了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.62,0:04:51.33,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我明白了 只要用這個力度的話…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.08,0:04:54.63,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？ 你剛剛說什麼？
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.33,0:04:56.09,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛才說
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.79,0:05:00.05,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,輸了的人要給贏了的人暖手
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.01,0:05:05.80,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,誒——
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.10,0:05:13.35,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你笑得太誇張了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.52,0:05:17.40,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你也太弱了吧 西片
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.98,0:05:20.53,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那就要玩懲罰遊戲了哦
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.11,0:05:22.24,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要幹什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.99,0:05:25.82,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不是說了嘛 輸了的人要給贏了的人暖手啊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.87,0:05:27.95,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 那是認真的嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.75,0:05:32.71,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,可…可以換成別的嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.50,0:05:34.29,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.21,0:05:36.38,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我也說不清
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.29,0:05:38.21,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那不行
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.46,0:05:41.21,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.77,0:05:56.56,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,給我暖寶寶
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.77,0:05:57.23,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.28,0:06:04.99,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.20,0:06:06.07,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝啦
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.87,0:06:08.95,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真暖和啊
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.09,0:06:16.96,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,外觀
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.67,0:06:20.76,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 西片
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.55,0:06:25.34,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 高木同學 早上好
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.56,0:06:30.18,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.48,0:06:34.23,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你臉上一副寫著「我想到有趣的比賽了」的表情嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.69,0:06:37.11,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,現在則是「你猜對了」的表情
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.48,0:06:39.98,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是高木同學
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.23,0:06:41.90,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,所以是什麼比賽啊
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.40,0:06:45.95,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 反正今天我一定能贏
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.20,0:06:49.45,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那今天的我和昨天有哪裡不一樣呢
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.74,0:06:51.45,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,來猜吧 是哪裡呢
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.04,0:06:57.50,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不是心情上的變化吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.59,0:06:58.75,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是外觀哦
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.26,0:07:04.18,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道了吧 高木同學
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.72,0:07:08.51,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,其實昨晚我剪了一點點頭髮
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.10,0:07:11.85,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然有點犯規 倒不如說是有點卑鄙
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.85,0:07:13.14,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,但贏了就是贏了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.69,0:07:15.77,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像知道了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.81,0:07:16.48,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.52,0:07:20.15,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我再觀察一會兒吧
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.32,0:07:22.57,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道吧
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.99,0:07:26.86,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是想等著我自己說漏嘴吧 可惡的高木同學
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.41,0:07:28.91,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會讓你得逞的
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.62,0:07:38.25,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真的有哪裡不一樣了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.71,0:07:40.46,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.38,0:07:42.67,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是背面嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.42,0:07:44.30,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.68,0:07:48.97,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到會被她這樣盯著看
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.18,0:07:54.06,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.52,0:07:56.06,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我想會不會是在衣服裡面
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.19,0:07:58.56,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦 是能看見的地方啦
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.06,0:08:00.48,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你太一驚一乍了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.23,0:08:06.20,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒想到中途會被這樣捉弄
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.28,0:08:13.54,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,腰這裡還是老樣子怕癢呢
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.83,0:08:15.33,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你只是想這麼幹吧
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.25,0:08:23.71,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,太…太近了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.51,0:08:25.97,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為是眼睛呢
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.97,0:08:30.47,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 你臉很紅哦
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.01,0:08:34.14,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不一樣的難道是臉紅嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.35,0:08:39.02,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,身上的味道呢
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.07,0:08:44.73,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,沒怎麼變啊
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.90,0:08:47.36,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說了嘛 是外觀 外觀
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.45,0:08:50.20,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是哪裡呢
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.53,0:08:55.79,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,難道高木同學其實已經知道了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.75,0:08:59.83,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,只是為了好玩捉弄我嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.13,0:09:03.29,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,難道我已經被看穿了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.63,0:09:07.51,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這些我都完全沒想到啊
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.39,0:09:12.72,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是眼睛吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.31,0:09:15.22,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 西片
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.22,0:09:18.85,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,如果害羞的話 也可以認輸哦
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.44,0:09:21.73,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不要
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.94,0:09:24.73,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.15,0:09:28.19,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,故意說要我放棄的話
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.49,0:09:30.78,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,就說明她並不知道答案
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.24,0:09:35.66,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說只要堅持過這一關 就是我的勝利了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.33,0:09:42.33,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是哪裡呢
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.21,0:09:45.09,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是耳朵嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.00,0:09:47.00,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不對啊
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.55,0:09:51.80,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,時間到
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.22,0:09:54.26,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,來這招啊
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.47,0:09:55.35,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,答案是什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.56,0:09:58.39,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,頭髮
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.02,0:10:06.77,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.86,0:10:11.45,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,能短時間改變的只有指甲和頭髮啊
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.99,0:10:13.20,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是指甲的話
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.20,0:10:14.16,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我想應該就是頭髮吧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.74,0:10:19.62,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那作為懲罰
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.20,0:10:23.04,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,明天我也做點外觀上的改變哦
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.21,0:10:25.17,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來輪到西片來猜哦
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.17,0:10:28.55,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡的高木同學
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.13,0:10:32.34,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,明知道我會害羞 不好意思盯著她看
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.05,0:10:34.89,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧走吧 去學校吧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.09,0:10:35.89,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要遲到了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.43,0:10:40.68,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒想到會被她反過來捉弄
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.19,0:10:50.82,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,天氣變冷了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.11,0:10:51.74,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.07,0:10:55.03,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,早…早上好
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.62,0:10:58.62,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,瀏海
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.21,0:11:11.34,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你瀏海怎麼回事啊 有點奇怪誒
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.34,0:11:12.84,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不許笑
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.59,0:11:18.55,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天自己剪了一下 結果剪多了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.26,0:11:21.68,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了 不許笑啦
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.18,0:11:26.90,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 太好笑了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.77,0:11:30.40,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你瀏海不也像剪毀了一樣
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.86,0:11:36.82,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真…真的嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.57,0:11:39.95,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊 差不多
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.08,0:11:46.67,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,失敗品一樣的瀏海…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.83,0:11:50.04,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,明明我還挺喜歡的…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.96,0:11:55.84,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 美奈 我有點說過頭了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.55,0:11:58.76,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那個瀏海很適合你哦
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.22,0:12:01.47,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.18,0:12:05.68,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是朋友的話明明應該要鼓勵你的
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.94,0:12:08.19,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我卻嘲笑了你
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.86,0:12:13.15,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起啊 由加莉
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.05,0:12:20.93,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.18,0:12:23.89,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,2月14日
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.64,0:12:25.56,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.72,0:12:26.27,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.27,0:12:29.73,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 今天也很冷呢
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.69,0:12:33.06,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,早…早上好 高木同學
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.69,0:12:34.52,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.61,0:12:37.44,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,情人節
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.24,0:12:42.70,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜下來啊我
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.20,0:12:45.78,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,平常心 要保持平常心啊
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.45,0:12:47.75,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 西片
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.83,0:12:48.91,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.41,0:12:51.58,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,今天有體育課嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.34,0:12:58.80,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得好像沒有
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.51,0:13:01.68,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是呢 謝謝你
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.85,0:13:11.81,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說 這裡面
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.14,0:13:14.31,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,會有某人塞進來的巧克力什麼的
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.82,0:13:20.94,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有啊
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.86,0:13:22.78,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 西片
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.49,0:13:24.03,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.53,0:13:27.49,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才打開鞋櫃時你好像有點失望
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.04,0:13:28.95,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.58,0:13:33.21,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…不… 沒…沒什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.62,0:13:35.63,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事…都沒有啦
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.05,0:13:41.63,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,紫式部的源氏物語
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.80,0:13:46.51,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,清少納言的枕草子也是研究對象之一
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.05,0:13:49.56,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,老師在讀中學的時候也…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.31,0:13:53.06,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不 就算是情人節
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.14,0:13:54.94,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我也沒抱有什麼期待哦
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.73,0:13:58.86,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊 倒不如說正是這種日子
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.90,0:14:00.73,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,她才更可能會來捉弄我
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.07,0:14:02.99,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,提高警戒吧
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.90,0:14:04.91,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 西片
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.03,0:14:06.16,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.49,0:14:08.08,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,能借我一下橡皮擦嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.95,0:14:09.58,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.20,0:14:14.29,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這難道是
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.79,0:14:18.50,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,在還我橡皮擦的時候 若無其事地遞給我巧克力
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.88,0:14:20.38,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣的話要怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.80,0:14:21.34,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.05,0:14:22.63,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.80,0:14:24.51,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.64,0:14:34.64,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,他這麼說耶 太好笑了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.19,0:14:35.77,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.44,0:14:40.02,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,然後啊…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.52,0:14:41.98,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎麼送給他呢
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.99,0:14:43.65,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,大家！
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.28,0:14:47.91,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是情人節 我做了很多巧克力
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.70,0:14:51.62,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,想要的人請自便
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.54,0:14:56.83,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人的吧 飽含愛意的手製巧克力？女子力好高
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.37,0:14:59.88,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要 我也要
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.92,0:15:06.51,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,像這樣四處散播自己的愛
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.18,0:15:08.01,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃的哦
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.22,0:15:09.05,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.64,0:15:11.81,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,給我好好地派給大家啊 日比野
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.10,0:15:13.85,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能去拿啊
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.68,0:15:17.77,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我要是也有美奈那樣的性格就好了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.78,0:15:25.32,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦發現巧克力就要沒收
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.74,0:15:28.57,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我說過了吧 日比野
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.12,0:15:34.79,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,沒收
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.58,0:15:37.96,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.29,0:15:41.46,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 還得小心老師才行
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.46,0:15:43.84,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我能送出去嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.05,0:15:47.55,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,沒收什麼的 好過分啊
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.67,0:15:50.14,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,明明我還沒拿到…
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.30,0:15:53.81,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真是聞者落淚呢 四處散播愛的後果
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.81,0:15:57.68,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,巧克力？
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.69,0:16:02.15,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 想問你是不是已經送出去了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.98,0:16:07.11,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要問有沒有送出去的話 也算是送出去了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.86,0:16:09.03,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼做到的？
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.40,0:16:10.03,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,早上…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.66,0:16:13.62,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣真的好嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.87,0:16:14.28,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.41,0:16:20.92,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,高木也覺得害羞嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.00,0:16:24.67,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我無論如何也想親手送給他
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.92,0:16:29.38,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺這樣才能表達我的心意
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.55,0:16:34.18,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 這簡直就像是試煉啊
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.06,0:16:37.77,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,就在海邊啊
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.77,0:16:38.56,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.64,0:16:39.43,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,來看看吧
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.69,0:16:42.15,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對很厲害的
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.19,0:16:43.36,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 真少見啊
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.81,0:16:44.44,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.02,0:16:45.77,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,中井君
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.15,0:16:47.03,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 真野
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.32,0:16:50.61,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,對 這是試煉啊
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.57,0:16:53.07,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能克服這個試煉
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.57,0:16:56.45,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我們之間的羈絆就會更加堅固…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.79,0:16:58.04,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊 中井
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.41,0:17:00.50,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,女朋友給你送巧克力來了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.66,0:17:01.21,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.29,0:17:03.50,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真羨慕你啊
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.17,0:17:12.76,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼生氣了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.48,0:17:21.23,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,做不到
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.31,0:17:23.52,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,做不到做不到做不到 絕對做不到的
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.73,0:17:26.77,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,再說那算什麼啊 整天和其他男生混在一起
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.90,0:17:28.90,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,明明知道我要送他巧克力吧
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.23,0:17:32.82,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,給我聰明點單獨行動啊 真是的
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.41,0:17:41.66,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,他是不是其實壓根不怎麼想要我的巧克力啊
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.37,0:17:45.21,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋！
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.33,0:17:45.92,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真野
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.80,0:17:51.84,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你突然跑開 我就追過來了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.39,0:17:57.80,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你在生什麼氣啊
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.43,0:17:59.31,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,太遲鈍了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.48,0:18:02.31,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起啊
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.98,0:18:10.15,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,巧克力 想要嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.57,0:18:12.24,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 想要
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.74,0:18:18.53,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.08,0:18:27.04,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要被沒收了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.38,0:18:27.92,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.00,0:18:28.63,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是書
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.09,0:18:31.67,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,她只是把借走的書還給我了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.47,0:18:40.81,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是書的話就算了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.86,0:18:50.48,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,緊張死了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.23,0:18:53.07,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你了 我很高興
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.03,0:19:01.28,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你還在生氣嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.70,0:19:03.50,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,遲鈍遲鈍遲鈍遲鈍
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.13,0:19:14.26,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,忽然感覺好累啊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.92,0:19:15.51,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.51,0:19:19.97,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,早知道就去要日比野的巧克力了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.68,0:19:22.31,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那個拉不下臉去要啊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.10,0:19:26.39,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要北條同學的巧克力
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.06,0:19:30.15,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,反正西片你已經收到高木同學的了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.15,0:19:31.48,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？不…
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.48,0:19:35.36,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊 我不想聽 饒了我吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.20,0:19:46.71,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,再…再見了 高木同學
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.16,0:19:47.58,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.05,0:19:55.46,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,結果什麼都沒有給我
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.13,0:19:58.93,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,還能還給你 太好了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.18,0:19:59.97,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,給我一個
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.14,0:20:01.85,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你們倆都嚐嚐看吧
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.35,0:20:05.72,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我也沒期待什麼的
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.27,0:20:11.19,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒因為到了情人節而被她捉弄
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.65,0:20:13.02,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,今天算是大勝利了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.12,0:20:23.70,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.58,0:20:25.54,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是巧克力？
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.66,0:20:29.00,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,什… 那個…這個是…
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.37,0:20:33.75,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是木村吧 大概是木村的惡作劇吧
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.92,0:20:34.42,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不是哦
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.42,0:20:37.59,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 為什麼這麼說
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.09,0:20:41.09,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我知道放這個進去的是誰
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.05,0:20:46.14,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 你覺得是誰？
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.06,0:20:51.19,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得她現在還離你挺近的呢
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.39,0:20:54.77,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這感覺 是高木同學吧
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.48,0:20:58.53,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不 但萬一不是的話…
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.07,0:21:01.40,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 還會很丟人
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.70,0:21:04.28,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想知道啦
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.49,0:21:05.28,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.70,0:21:10.00,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道今天是什麼日子吧
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.54,0:21:13.46,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,情人節
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.54,0:21:16.21,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？你說什麼？
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.09,0:21:17.92,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,情人節！
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.88,0:21:19.92,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,答對了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.59,0:21:22.59,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那給你巧克力哦
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.30,0:21:24.64,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？不要嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.18,0:21:27.68,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是那樣的
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.27,0:21:29.85,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要給我巧克力？
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.39,0:21:34.52,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說 這個不是高木同學給我的嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.02,0:21:35.52,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.52,0:21:39.11,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你…
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.61,0:21:41.40,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是義理的哦
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.90,0:21:42.90,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的啦
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.74,0:21:44.61,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我說的是這個
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.62,0:21:46.49,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,「這個」？
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.41,0:21:48.91,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那這一個是？
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.42,0:22:03.63,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那個巧克力 你知道是誰送的麼
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.84,0:22:06.01,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,誰…誰知道呢
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.85,0:22:08.35,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道也行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.09,0:01:34.30,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,寒いね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.51,0:01:37.22,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,手がかじかんできちゃったね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.89,0:01:39.76,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,寒いの苦手だからなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.90,0:01:47.98,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,カイロ使う?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.77,0:01:51.57,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,大丈夫　ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.03,0:01:52.74,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,そっか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.91,0:02:02.83,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,氷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.12,0:02:07.92,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,でかい氷だな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.21,0:02:10.09,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,昨日雨だったもんね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.63,0:02:18.68,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,“持っていきたい”とか思ってる?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.80,0:02:19.93,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,思ってないよ!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.14,0:02:22.81,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,そんな 小学生じゃあるまいし
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.10,0:02:26.35,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ホントかな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.69,0:02:32.78,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ねえ 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.90,0:02:36.07,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,勝負しよっか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.53,0:02:39.41,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,いいけど 何するの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.91,0:02:43.16,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,校門まで  大きい氷を持っていったほうの勝ち
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.70,0:02:46.79,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ただし 地面に落としちゃったら  その時点で負け
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.79,0:02:48.42,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,どう?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.96,0:02:51.71,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,いいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.96,0:02:52.96,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,お先にどうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:02:56.34,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃ 俺は…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.55,0:03:01.68,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,大きいの取ったね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.85,0:03:04.64,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,学校まで もてばいいけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.31,0:03:08.52,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,高木さんめ 焦っているな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.98,0:03:11.48,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,悪いが 俺が  この氷を落とすことはない!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.11,0:03:16.82,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,なぜなら 俺は小さいころから氷を見つけると必ず持ち運んでいたから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.90,0:03:18.82,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,指が冷たさに強いのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:22.83,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,よって俺の手がかじかんで氷を離すことはない!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.87,0:03:27.00,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,加えて  高木さんにからかわれた回数の３倍の腕立てを
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:29.33,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,厳しく  自分に課している俺にとって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.37,0:03:32.50,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,こんな氷 大した重さじゃないのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:36.71,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,思いつき勝負を仕掛けたことを  後悔するがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:39.34,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,高木さんは今日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:41.51,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,俺に負ける!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.27,0:03:48.77,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:50.69,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ううん　ちょっとね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.77,0:03:54.52,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,なんか 西片が大きい氷持って
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.57,0:03:56.86,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,うれしがってる小学生みたいだなって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:59.65,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,なっ…  別に うれしがってなんか…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:06.04,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,危なっ!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:09.66,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,惜しかったな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.17,0:04:13.08,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,高木さんめ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:15.17,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,うかつだった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:18.17,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,“落とさせる”  そんな作戦があったか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:22.80,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,絶対にもう気は抜かないぞ  今日こそ勝つんだ!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:27.39,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,そんなに力強く握ると  割れちゃうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.27,0:04:31.94,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,敵の心配か?  余裕だな 高木さんめ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.69,0:04:33.44,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,いや…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.11,0:04:38.69,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,でも確かに あまり力を入れて割れてしまっては
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.78,0:04:42.78,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,そうだ　罰ゲームだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:47.37,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,“負けたほうが  勝ったほうの手を温かくする”ね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:51.33,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,よし 分かった  このくらいの力加減か
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:54.63,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,えっ?　今何て?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.33,0:04:56.09,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,だからね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.79,0:05:00.05,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,負けたほうは  勝ったほうの手を温かくするの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:05.80,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,えーっ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.10,0:05:13.35,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,笑い過ぎだろう!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.52,0:05:17.40,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,弱いなぁ 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:20.53,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃ 罰ゲームね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:22.24,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,何すんの?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.99,0:05:25.82,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,だから 勝ったほうの手 温めるの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.87,0:05:27.95,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,それ  ホントに言ってたの?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.75,0:05:32.71,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,べ… 別のにしない?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:34.29,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,なんで?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.21,0:05:36.38,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,なんとなく…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.29,0:05:38.21,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃ ダメ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.46,0:05:41.21,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.77,0:05:56.56,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,カイロちょうだい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:05:57.23,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,えっ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:04.99,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:06.07,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.87,0:06:08.95,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,温かいね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.09,0:06:16.96,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,外見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:20.76,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,おはよう 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.55,0:06:25.34,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,やあ 高木さん　おはよう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.56,0:06:30.18,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.48,0:06:34.23,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,“いい勝負 考えてきた”って  顔してるから
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.69,0:06:37.11,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,“当たり”って顔してる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.48,0:06:39.98,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,さすが高木さんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:41.90,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,…で 何の勝負なの?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:45.95,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,まあいい  今日こそ 俺の勝ちなんだからな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.20,0:06:49.45,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃ 俺は  昨日と どこか違っています
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.74,0:06:51.45,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,さて どこでしょう?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:06:57.50,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,気分とかじゃなくて?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.59,0:06:58.75,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,外見だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.26,0:07:04.18,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,分からないだろう?　高木さん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:08.51,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,実は昨日の夜  髪の毛を少しだけ切ったのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.10,0:07:11.85,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,反則スレスレ  ていうか卑怯くさいけど
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.85,0:07:13.14,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,勝ちは勝ちだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:15.77,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,分かったかも
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.81,0:07:16.48,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,はぁ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:20.15,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,でも もうちょっと観察しようかな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.32,0:07:22.57,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,分かってないな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.99,0:07:26.86,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,カマをかけて 俺の口が滑るのを狙っているな?　高木さんめ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.41,0:07:28.91,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,そうはいくか!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:38.25,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ホントに どこか違うの?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.71,0:07:40.46,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.38,0:07:42.67,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,後ろかなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:44.30,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,しまった!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:48.97,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ジロジロ見られることを 計算に入れてなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:54.06,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,何してんの!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.52,0:07:56.06,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,服の下かなと思って
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.19,0:07:58.56,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,違うよ!　見えるとこだよ!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:00.48,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,びっくりしすぎだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:06.20,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,途中でこんなふうにからかわれるのも  計算に入れてなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:13.54,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,いつもどおり弱いね 脇腹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.83,0:08:15.33,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,やりたかっただけだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:23.71,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ち… 近いよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.51,0:08:25.97,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,目かなと思って
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.97,0:08:30.47,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,あれ?　顔赤いよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:34.14,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,もしかして違うのって 顔の赤さ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.35,0:08:39.02,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,においはどうかな?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.07,0:08:44.73,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,普通だね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.90,0:08:47.36,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,だから 外見だって 外見!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.45,0:08:50.20,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,どこかなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:55.79,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,まさか高木さん  本当は答えが分かってるんじゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:08:59.83,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,俺をからかって  楽しんでいるだけなのでは?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.13,0:09:03.29,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,まさか見抜かれて?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.63,0:09:07.51,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,そんなの全く計算に入れてなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.39,0:09:12.72,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,やっぱり目かな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.31,0:09:15.22,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ねえ 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:18.85,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,恥ずかしいなら  ギブアップしてもいいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.44,0:09:21.73,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,絶対しない!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.94,0:09:24.73,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,いいけど
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:28.19,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,“ギブアップしてもいいよ”ってわざわざ言ってくるってことは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.49,0:09:30.78,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,答えが分かっていないってことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.24,0:09:35.66,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,つまり  ここを しのげば 俺の勝ちだ!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.33,0:09:42.33,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,どこかな?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.21,0:09:45.09,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,耳かな?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:47.00,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,違うかなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.55,0:09:51.80,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,タイムアップ!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.22,0:09:54.26,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,あっ…　そう来たか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.47,0:09:55.35,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,答えは?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.56,0:09:58.39,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,髪の毛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.02,0:10:06.77,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,なんで?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.86,0:10:11.45,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,すぐ変えられる外見なんて  爪か髪の毛ぐらいだし
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.99,0:10:13.20,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,爪じゃなかったら
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:14.16,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,髪かなって
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:19.62,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃ 罰ゲームだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:23.04,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,私もあした  ちょっと外見変えてくるから
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:25.17,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,次は西片が当ててね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.17,0:10:28.55,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,高木さんめ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.13,0:10:32.34,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,恥ずかしくてまじまじ見られないと分かってて…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:34.89,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ほらほら 学校行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.09,0:10:35.89,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,遅れちゃうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.43,0:10:40.68,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,やり返されるのも  計算に入れてなかった…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.19,0:10:50.82,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,寒くなったねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.11,0:10:51.74,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.07,0:10:55.03,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,お… おはよう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.62,0:10:58.62,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,前髪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.21,0:11:11.34,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,どうしたの?　その髪　何か変
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.34,0:11:12.84,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,わ… 笑うな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:18.55,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,昨日 ちょっと自分で切ってたら  切り過ぎちゃって…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.26,0:11:21.68,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,だから 笑うなって
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:26.90,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,いや ムリだよ  面白いんだもん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:30.40,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,あんただって  失敗したみたいな前髪のくせに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.86,0:11:36.82,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ほ… 本当に?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.57,0:11:39.95,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ そうよ　似たようなもんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,0:11:46.67,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,失敗したみたいな前髪…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.83,0:11:50.04,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,結構 気に入ってたのに…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.96,0:11:55.84,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ごめん ミナ　ちょっと言い過ぎた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.55,0:11:58.76,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,似合ってるよ その前髪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.22,0:12:01.47,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,私のほうこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:05.68,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,友達なら 励まさなきゃ  いけないとこだったのに…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.94,0:12:08.19,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,笑っちゃって…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.86,0:12:13.15,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ごめんね ユカリちゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:20.93,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,今日は…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.18,0:12:23.89,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,2月14日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:25.56,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,つまり…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:26.27,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.27,0:12:29.73,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,おはよう　今日も寒いね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.69,0:12:33.06,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,お… おはよう 高木さん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:34.52,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,つまり…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.61,0:12:37.44,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,バレンタインデー
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:42.70,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,落ち着け 俺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:45.78,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,平常心 平常心だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:47.75,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ねえ 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:48.91,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,な… なに
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.41,0:12:51.58,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,今日って 体育あったっけ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.34,0:12:58.80,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,いや　なかったと思うけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.51,0:13:01.68,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,そうだよね　ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:11.81,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,もしかして この中に
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:14.31,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,誰かからのチョコが入っていたり…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:20.94,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,…しないよな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:22.78,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ねえ 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:24.03,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,な… なに!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:27.49,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,今 ゲタ箱開けてちょっとがっかりしてたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.04,0:13:28.95,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,どうかしたの?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:33.21,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,あっ いや…べ… 別に…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:35.63,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,何でもないから
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:41.63,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,紫式部の「源氏物語」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:46.51,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,清少納言の「枕草子」も  研究の対象となっていました
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:49.56,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,先生も中学のときには…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.31,0:13:53.06,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,い…いや…バレンタインだからって
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:54.94,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,別に期待してるわけじゃないぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.73,0:13:58.86,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,そうだ  むしろこんな日だからこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:00.73,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,俺を からかってくるはずだ!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.07,0:14:02.99,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,気をつけよう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:04.91,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ねえ 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:06.16,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,は… はい!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:08.08,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,消しゴム 貸してくれない?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:09.58,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,いいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.20,0:14:14.29,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,これは もしや
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:18.50,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,消しゴムを返すついでに  さりげな?くチョコなんかを…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:20.38,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,だったら どうしよう!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:21.34,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.05,0:14:22.63,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:24.51,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,うん…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.64,0:14:34.64,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,そう言ったんだよ  それって笑えるだろう?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.19,0:14:35.77,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,だな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:40.02,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,でさ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:41.98,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,どうやって渡そう…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.99,0:14:43.65,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,みんな?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:47.91,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,今日 バレンタインだから  チョコいっぱい作ってきたよ!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:51.62,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,欲しい人は どうぞ!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.54,0:14:56.83,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ウソ!?　愛の手作りチョコ?  女子力 たかっ!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:14:59.88,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,あっ 私 欲しい!私も!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:06.51,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,あんなに愛をばらまいて…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.18,0:15:08.01,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,おいしいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:09.05,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.64,0:15:11.81,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ちゃんと配れよ 日々野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.10,0:15:13.85,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,もらいに行けるわけねえだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:17.77,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,私も  ミナちゃんみたいな性格だったらな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.78,0:15:25.32,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,“チョコは見つけしだい没収”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.74,0:15:28.57,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,そう言ったよな?　日々野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:34.79,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,没収
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:37.96,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,先生!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:41.46,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,そっか　先生にも気をつけないと
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:43.84,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,渡せるのかな…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.05,0:15:47.55,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ひどいよ 没収なんて…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:50.14,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,私 まだもらってないのに…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:53.81,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,泣きを見るのね  むやみに愛をばらまくと
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:15:57.68,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,チョコ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.69,0:16:02.15,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,うん　もう渡したのかなって…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:07.11,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,渡したっていえば 渡したのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:09.03,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ど… どうやって?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:10.03,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,朝…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.66,0:16:13.62,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,いいの?　それで
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.87,0:16:14.28,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:20.92,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,高木ちゃんも恥ずかしいのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:24.67,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,でも 私は手渡ししたい  なんとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:29.38,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,そのほうが  気持ちが伝わる気がするし
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:34.18,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,でも  これじゃ まるで試練だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.06,0:16:37.77,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,海沿いにあるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.77,0:16:38.56,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,マジか!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:39.43,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,見てこいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.69,0:16:42.15,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,絶対すごいって
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.19,0:16:43.36,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,へえ…　珍しいな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:44.44,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,あの…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:45.77,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,中井君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:47.03,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,おう 真野
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.32,0:16:50.61,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,そう　試練よ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:53.07,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,これを乗り越えれば
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.57,0:16:56.45,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,私たちの絆は より強く…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.79,0:16:58.04,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,いいな 中井
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:00.50,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,彼女からチョコだぞ これ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:01.21,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,おい!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:03.50,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,羨ましい!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:12.76,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,なんで怒ってんだ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.48,0:17:21.23,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ムリ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:23.52,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ムリムリムリ!　絶対ムリ!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:26.77,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,…ていうか なんなの!?  いっつも男子と一緒にいてさ!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:28.90,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,チョコ渡すって分かるでしょう!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:32.82,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,気を利かせて  1人行動くらいしてよね! もう?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:41.66,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,私のチョコ 別に欲しくないのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:45.21,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,バカ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:45.92,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,真野
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.80,0:17:51.84,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,急に逃げるから追っかけてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.39,0:17:57.80,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,なあ　なに怒ってんだよ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:17:59.31,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,鈍感!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.48,0:18:02.31,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ごめんな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:10.15,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,チョコ  要る?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:12.24,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ　欲しいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:18.53,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:27.04,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,没収…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.38,0:18:27.92,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,おい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:28.63,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,本です!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.09,0:18:31.67,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,貸してた本  返してもらってただけで…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:40.81,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,本なら まあいいか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.86,0:18:50.48,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,緊張した
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:53.07,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとな　うれしいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.03,0:19:01.28,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,なあ　まだ怒ってんのか?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:03.50,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,鈍感 鈍感 鈍感 鈍感
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:14.26,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,なんか どっと疲れたな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:15.51,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.51,0:19:19.97,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,日々野のチョコ  もらっとくんだったぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:22.31,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,あれはもらえねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.10,0:19:26.39,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,俺は  北条さんにもらいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.06,0:19:30.15,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,どうせ西片は高木さんにもらったんだろう?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.15,0:19:31.48,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,えっ?　いや…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.48,0:19:35.36,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,アーッ!　アア…　聞きたくない!やめてくれ!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:46.71,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃ… じゃあね 高木さん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:47.58,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.05,0:19:55.46,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,結局 何もなかったー!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:19:58.93,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,良かったね 返してもらえて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.18,0:19:59.97,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ちょうだい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.14,0:20:01.85,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,2人とも食べて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.35,0:20:05.72,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,いや…  別に期待なんてしてなかったさ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.27,0:20:11.19,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,バレンタインのことで  からかわれなかったんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.65,0:20:13.02,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,今日は大勝利さ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:23.70,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.58,0:20:25.54,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,あっ チョコ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.66,0:20:29.00,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,なっ…　え?っと これは…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:33.75,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,き…木村かな  多分 木村のいたずらじゃないかな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:34.42,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,違うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:37.59,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,えっ?な… なんで?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:41.09,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,だって  私 それ入れたの誰か知ってるし
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:46.14,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ねえ  誰だと思う?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.06,0:20:51.19,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,今 結構近くにいると思うな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.39,0:20:54.77,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,こ… この感じは 高木さんだな?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:58.53,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,いや　でも 万が一にも違ったら…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:01.40,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,それに なんか恥ずかしいし
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:04.28,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,べ…別に知りたくないし
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:05.28,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ふ?ん
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.70,0:21:10.00,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,今日って 何の日か知ってる?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.54,0:21:13.46,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,バレンタイン…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:16.21,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,う?ん?　なぁに?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.09,0:21:17.92,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,バレンタイン!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:19.92,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,正解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:22.59,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃ チョコあげるね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:24.64,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,うん?　要らない?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:27.68,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,いや　別に そういうんじゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.27,0:21:29.85,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,チョコをくれる?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.39,0:21:34.52,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,…てことは  これは高木さんからじゃないのか?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.02,0:21:35.52,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.52,0:21:39.11,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:41.40,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,義理だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:42.90,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,分かってるよ!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.74,0:21:44.61,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,こっちはね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.62,0:21:46.49,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,“こっちは”?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.41,0:21:48.91,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃ こっちは?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:03.63,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,そのチョコ 誰からか分かる?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.84,0:22:06.01,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,さ… さあ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.85,0:22:08.35,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,分からなくていいから
